==Village Idiot==
===Overview===
:    A Village idiot is a term used for non-handicapped people, being at least 18 years of age, with mental capabilites equal too or inferior to that of two year old. An important fact not always noted when studying these lifeforms is that very Village has its own idiot and every idiot has his own villiage. Also worth condidering is the fact village idiots, though not necessarily willing, do many things to attain and maintain their idiot status. 
:    Unfortunately, this alarming surge of Village Idiocity is spiralling downward because of decreased worldwide intelligence levels. This frightful trend does not only link itself to the American culture but has spread throughout the world via extensive village idiot networks.